Federal Register: 197. 1,4-Phenylenediamine dihydrochloride (CAS No. 000624-18-0) (RCRA APP8) (Ref. 8). Measured aquatic acute toxicity for 1,4-phenylenediamine include a fish 96-hour LC sub 50 of 60 ppb. EPA believes that there is sufficient evidence for listing 1,4-phenylenediamine dihydrochloride on EPCRA section 313 pursuant to EPCRA section 313(d)(2)(C) based on the available environmental toxicity data for 1,4-phenylenediamine.
